<item>
            <title>[LU-17698] Debian 12: lustre-*-dbgsym_$${VER}_*.ddeb: No such file or directory</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17698</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On Debian 12, DBGSYM_PACKAGE_TYPE is defined the same as DEFAULT_PACKAGE_TYPE, which is &apos;deb&apos; instead of &apos;ddeb&apos; in Dh_Lib.pm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, the suffix of the dbgsym debug symbol packages is &apos;.deb&apos;, and the changes in &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/53378&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/53378&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17347&quot; title=&quot;make debs is ignoring some output files (ddeb)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17347&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17347&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; debs: also move .ddeb files into debs/&quot;) will be causing the following build failure:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mv: cannot stat &apos;../lustre-*-dbgsym_2.15.61-194-g5cda4a3-1_*.ddeb&apos;: No such file or directory
make: *** [autoMakefile:1318: debs] Error 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
